Season 2 videos are NOT soothing to eyes, I am sorry to say. Please use season 1 videos as reference and compare.

Very flashy frames, very rapid change of frames and closeup shots instead of wide angle shots (you have a lot of talented artists, show them as much as you can in one footage rather than jumping from this to that frame)...... it felt like everyone is in a rush. Same thing happened in the video of “Bonobibi” too.

Directors, producers please produce videos which are sober and soothing to eyes.
